Infusion Events dataset

Source: R/patient_data.R
infusion_events.Rd

These datasets provide information about patients, infusion events, and end of study events. Trial data has been de-identified and randomized for general use.

Usage

data(infusion_events)

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 18 rows and 5 columns.

Source

This dataset is for demonstration purposes only.

Details

infusion_events contains pre-formatted time series data related to infusions and reinfusions for patients in patient_data. This dataset is most applicable for use with geom_swim_marker().
